    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/48163e398d7f19e80c2a31cb7f54da8c.avif?t=1741015939\" width=700 height=104 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你是否有勇气直面疯狂</strong></h2>在洛夫克拉夫特构筑的奇异世界中，展开一段疯狂的冒险旅程，不断与你的内心交流并做出抉择，每一个选项都将让故事流向不同的方向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/b1ce8b941c22ca50959ee203420d9733.poster.avif?t=1741015939\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/b1ce8b941c22ca50959ee203420d9733.webm?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/b1ce8b941c22ca50959ee203420d9733.mp4?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸于文字构筑的奇妙世界中</strong></h2>所见为实，放飞想象。游戏中有着超过14万字的剧情文本，300多幅手绘图片以及全新的原创曲目。放松身心，让你的想象力起航，跟随军医杰克·亨廷顿一同前往1896年的桑给巴尔，病毒、神秘宗教以及潜藏于阴影之下的神秘存在将逐渐显露它们的身影。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/4722d6a7ad43a50d8394359655901785.poster.avif?t=1741015939\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/4722d6a7ad43a50d8394359655901785.webm?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/4722d6a7ad43a50d8394359655901785.mp4?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事走向由你来决定</strong></h2>在故事的过程中，可能充斥着大量的死亡，你的每一个选择都有可能决定着其他人物的生死。在大多数时候死亡都是不可避免的，不过在故事过程中你的选择可能会产生比死亡本身更加严重的后果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/105d98724130e5f1566742b135a93d63.poster.avif?t=1741015939\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/105d98724130e5f1566742b135a93d63.webm?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/105d98724130e5f1566742b135a93d63.mp4?t=1741015939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/e1f7b57bc334d73023e64d79d9a547cc.avif?t=1741015939\" width=700 height=104 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>见证比远古更加久远的邪恶存在</strong></h2><br>死亡的阴霾笼罩在非洲大陆上，在这片神秘的土地上，深入探寻病毒的根源，你会发现一切的线索似乎都指向了一个更加古老且邪恶的存在。它在阴影中之下悄然滋长，它的触手遍及全世界。而你将在经历重重冒险之后，揭露最终的真相的。<br><br>永远都要记住，过度地窥探真相，可能会让你深陷其中。或许脱身的最好方式就是远离这一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668590/extras/974d283aee9e75e5e0563f5a4130a24d.avif?t=1741015939\" width=700 height=86 /></span>",
